<bibRefCitation pageId="9" pageNumber="36">ThripsWiki 2013</bibRefCitation>
), of which five species are known from Iran (
<bibRefCitation pageId="9" pageNumber="36">Bhatti et al. 2009a</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Thripidae" genus="Oxythrips" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Oxythrips" order="Thysanoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Oxythrips</taxonomicName>
